Package: ppos
Title: Calculates predictive probability of success (PPoS) for making a go-no-go decision
Imports: 
        R2jags,
        meta,
        assertthat,
        forestplot,
        dplyr,
        stringr
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Archie Sachdeva <archiesachdeva.uf@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Archie Sachdeva <archiesachdeva.uf@gmail.com>
Description: This package computes predictive probability (PPoS) of future trial success given data from the historical trials on similar drugs or treatments.
